      <p begin="01:17:59.333" end="01:18:00.916">you're participating in a structured</p>
      <p begin="01:18:00.916" end="01:18:02.333">informational ecosystem.</p>
      <p begin="01:18:02.750" end="01:18:03.166">So you want to</p>
